column5: I've had dial up for the last 6 months. It is good to get high speed back!
welcome back to the speedy life lol
I'd rather not have a computer than have dial-up.

I know how you feel...I waited for four years for Ma Bell to put hi-speed in this area and finally gave up...contacted my cable company...and by bundling my tv cable...I ended up saving approx $35 a month...
